{"tid":194074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"火爆男出連環拳 商場保安勸交被打至昏迷","createTime":"2017-04-09T17:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T19:06:19.000Z","uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b99f63ec2e64c0d1c5ce0f47b82ec9358ce80ae7","tid":194074,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:15:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170409&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56542997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170409%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56542997&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=02ff8fd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170409%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56542997&h=93f53a9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170409&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56542997</a><br />\n調景嶺商場都會駅發生毆鬥傷人案。下午4時許，商場管理公司獲悉有人在都會駅二樓豪宴海鮮酒家內爭執，派出保安到場勸止，其中一名身穿藍衣的肥胖男突然遷怒於保安，將他打傷。《蘋果》取得一段街坊拍攝的現場短片所見，顯示該名涉嫌打人的藍衣肥胖男連環向男保安施以六、七記重拳，躺在地上的男保安無力還擊，抽搐身體痛苦呻吟，當時有街坊大叫：「你做咩打人？」之後有數名途人合力隔開及制服該名肥胖男，包括一名洋籍男大嚷：「call the police！」據知，男保安事後昏迷，有附近診所醫生及護士聞訊，前往事發現場為傷者治理。警方接報到場調查，以涉嫌襲擊導致他人受傷拘捕涉案肥胖男，傷者則送伊利沙伯醫院治理。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/10/011500_055649199dfadd45095418cbc75db667.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F10%2F011500_055649199dfadd45095418cbc75db667.jpg&h=4324d69e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f23eb1f4cbab6bad718be900eaacc250530d4de3","tid":194074,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:16:12.000Z","msg":"姑娘坐姿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4b4024d51133bbb23e07d20e0ee01107fd5ded","tid":194074,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"咁就誤殺坐3-4 碌 <br />\n出返黎做返保安啦手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c4ea7a80482ed7297899da1663328c0d78982e","tid":194074,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T19:06:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姑娘坐姿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n引人奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}